                    <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        <span class="text-tech-blue font-bold">SYMBOL SCIENCES, Inc.</span> is the pioneering company in the field of bar coding and automatic identification technologies in the Philippines.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
