                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold font-grotesk text-white">Advanced Solutions</h4>
                            <p class="text-white/70">Our solutions range from the supply of certified bar code images and high quality bar code labels to the manufacture of ISO compliant bar code verifies.</p>
